asset_contract.name: FLUF
asset_contract.description:
This is FLUF World…

A metaverse ecosystem of NFT character collectables and a global, creative community. From our genesis collection Flufs, to Thingies, Party Bears and more to come, we’re building a world that’s yours to shape, explore and call home. 

Flufs are the collection that started it all. 10,000 3D rabbit avatars, programmatically-generated from over 270 traits! Unique by at least three degrees of separation, Flufs are yours to trade, collect and customise through our growing Scenes & Sounds collection. 

But Flufs aren’t just furry faces... Metaverse-ready and full of surprises, they’re your ticket to a world of exclusive content, digital connectivity, IRL experiences and more.

Welcome to the Fluffle. 

---

**Official Collections:**

[FLUF World: Thingies](https://opensea.io/collection/fluf-world-thingies)

[FLUF World: Burrows](https://opensea.io/collection/fluf-world-burrows)

[FLUF World: Scenes & Sounds](https://opensea.io/collection/fluf-world-scenes-and-sounds)

name: Harley Yakuza Quinn
description: Growing up, Harley the young Fluf has always been fond of Batman comics and cartoon. She had a strange connection with one of Batmans arch nemesis, the Joker. She would have random dreams becoming Jokers wife and at times waking up bobbing her head to the tune of her favourite song, Run Rabbit. She realised her mother, an unknown Fluf in her distant memory, had named her Harley Quinn, who happened to be Jokers girlfriend in the Batman comics. Ever since then, Harley decided she wants to take on the Joker persona since she was born with a clown nose and peppermint fur which resembled Jokers features. When she woke up from her slumber during the great Fluf hibernation, she migrated to Tokyo and formed her own alliance with the Yakuza where she lived her fantasies in reality as a ruthless gang leader. While killing enemy gang members, you can hear her listening to Run Rabbit while bobbing her head, though she will always look fierce even when she is happy, since she is still single. So to the other badass male Flufs, if you think you are cool enough for Harley, you can try your luck to woo her! If not... we recommend you to stay far away. Or you will realise the true meaning of her middle name...

name: Hef Flufner
description: Hugh, They call him the big hop, the thunder from down under, the lucky foot in the cowboy, the bunny out for honey aka Hugh Flufner or to his mates HEF Hef was born and breed in the great outback of Northern Territory, Australia.Working under his father as a station hand.Droving the cattle from the red plains to market was his family business.Hef thought this was the only way life was to be, until his father Peter died when his blue jacket got caught on the bordering fenceline of Mcgregors Orchard.Mr McGregor shot and killed Peter in broad daylight.With his father's death, the urge to drove also died inside Hef.He turned his back on the station life and joined the forces.He travelled the world donning his iconic cowboy hat protecting his country.Hef was known to be quite the party bunny hunting out the nights that turned to into days, indulging in nights of debauchery as a bise xual turning anything that moves into his warren.This was his new way of life until one fortunate three day beach Rave where Hef was offered a carrot from a young hunny bunny called Millie.Hef and Millie continued their relationship while Hef wound up his time in the forces. Hef had found the one, he dropped to his knee and put a ring on it. Before their wedding, Millie confessed that she had an affair while he was away on duty in the army.Hef admits that this is the most devastating moment of his life.Millie however now allows Hef to have relations with other bunnies, out of guilt for her own infidelity and in hope that it will preserve their marriage.Hef, remade himself as a bon vivant and man about town, building an empire based on his flair and a lifestyle that he soon promoted in his magazine and TV shows, known today as PlayFluf.

A metaverse ecosystem of NFT character collectables and a global, creative community. From our genesis collection Flufs, to Thingies, Party Bears and more to come, we’re building a world that’s yours to shape, explore and call home. 

Flufs are the collection that started it all. 10,000 3D rabbit avatars, programmatically-generated from over 270 traits! Unique by at least three degrees of separation, Flufs are yours to trade, collect and customise through our growing Scenes & Sounds collection.

Welcome to the Fluffle.

A metaverse ecosystem of NFT character collectables and a global, creative community. From our genesis collection Flufs, to Thingies, Party Bears and more to come, we’re building a world that’s yours to shape, explore and call home. 

Flufs are the collection that started it all. 10,000 3D rabbit avatars, programmatically-generated from over 270 traits! Unique by at least three degrees of separation, Flufs are yours to trade, collect and customise through our growing Scenes & Sounds collection. 

But Flufs aren’t just furry faces... Metaverse-ready and full of surprises, they’re your ticket to a world of exclusive content, digital connectivity, IRL experiences and more.

Welcome to the Fluffle. 

---

**Official Collections:**

[FLUF World: Thingies](https://opensea.io/collection/fluf-world-thingies)

[FLUF World: Burrows](https://opensea.io/collection/fluf-world-burrows)

[FLUF World: Scenes & Sounds](https://opensea.io/collection/fluf-world-scenes-and-sounds)
